reviewer: unbraind
risk: critical
confidence: 100
sprint: 2026-07-security-modernization
release: next
reporter: GitHub Dependabot
severity: critical
environment: development and CI dependency graph
repro_steps: Inspect bun.lock or run bun pm ls vitest; observe 1.6.1 below patched 3.2.6.
resolution: "Upgraded Vitest and @vitest/coverage-v8 together to 4.1.10; GitHub marked Dependabot alert #3 fixed at 2026-07-16T17:13:49Z."
expected_result: No dependency resolves a vulnerable Vitest version; tests and coverage remain green.
actual_result: "bun.lock resolves Vitest 4.1.10, 542 tests and coverage gates pass, production audits report zero vulnerabilities, and GHSA-5xrq-8626-4rwp is fixed."
